":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T13:24:13.000Z","msg":"性接觸傳染<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4d2e93b531a6ca95c7f667495aaa7cc31d51437","tid":2301670,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T13:24:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc152444e0e84d9f8f927ce4f154bb5fffaa087b","tid":2301670,"uid":45013,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T14:03:34.000Z","msg":"唔⋯⋯<br />\n咁有幾多死咗？幾多個肺花咗？幾多跳唔起1cm？<br />\n定係⋯⋯ 其實中咗自己都唔知，唔去check都唔知有病毒，即係冇病冇痛（咁好似連「病咗」都講唔上喎），又係唔係咳幾聲抖下又冇事？<br />\n講到咁嚴重，仲以為一有病毒就變喪屍添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45f4f7f8ffcfbc103ab2af1c06f68bf95f9d85e5","tid":2301670,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T14:05:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"47a9b915411314a8f0162f8ebe89ae83326fc142","tid":2301670,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T14:06:19.000Z","msg":"邊隊 ?"}]}